==逃亡经历==
1993年，卡拉季奇在访问联合国总部期间就接到了传票。不过美国政府没有在他于1995年访问联合国期间成功抓到他。<ref>''Kadić v. Karadžić'', 70 F.3d 232 (2d Cir. 1995)</ref>

有传言称，美国政府根据代顿协定对卡拉季奇提供了保护。不过，这并不妨碍卡拉季奇长达接近十年之久的逃亡令他在波黑塞族间的声望越来越高。
<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7062288.stm|title=Hague probes Karadzic 'deal' claim|publisher=BBC|accessdate=24 July 2008|date=26 October 2007|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225145246/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/7062288.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Radovan Karadzic 'was under US protection until 2000'|work=The Telegraph|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/serbia/2496948/Karadzic-was-under-US-protection.html|author=Jon Swaine|date=2008-08-04|accessdate=2015-07-13|location=London, UK|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308134635/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/europe/serbia/2496948/Karadzic-was-under-US-protection.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

在逃亡期间，卡拉季奇得到了包括{{le|Bosko Radonjich|Bosko Radonjich}}在内数人的帮助。2001年，数百名卡拉季奇支持者曾在卡拉季奇的家乡举行集会支持卡拉季奇。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.esquire.com/features/radovan-karadzic-1297|title=Radovan Karadzic: A Deeply Misunderstood Mass Murderer|accessdate=2008-07-28|publisher=Esquire|archive-date=2014-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141222015732/http://www.esquire.com/features/radovan-karadzic-1297|dead-url=no}}</ref>2003年3月，卡拉季奇的母亲约万卡公开劝说卡拉季奇投降。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/commentisfree/2006/jul/01/comment.warcrimes|title=Whatever happened to ... Radovan Karadzic?|work=The Guardian|location=London|accessdate=2008-07-24|date=2008-07-01|first=Iain|last=Hollingshead}}</ref>

英国官员称，相较于通过军事手段，在政治上向巴尔干国家政府施压更可能将卡拉季奇以及其他嫌犯抓获归案。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iiss.org/whats-new/iiss-in-the-press/july-2008/karadzic-snared-by-spy-tip-and-political-will/|title=Karadzic snared by spy tip and political will|publisher=The International Institute For Strategic Studies|accessdate=2008-07-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080813031615/http://www.iiss.org/whats-new/iiss-in-the-press/july-2008/karadzic-snared-by-spy-tip-and-political-will|archivedate=2008-08-04}}</ref>

2004年5月，联合国得知，一名向前南刑庭提供有关卡拉季奇消息的嫌犯的兄弟在塞族共和国警方发动的一起突袭行动中遭到误杀。联合国方面认为，策划者是想堵住那名嫌犯的嘴。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.unhcr.org/refworld/pdfid/42f736424.pdf|title=Update on Conditions for Return to Bosnia and Herzegovina (2005)|accessdate=2015-07-23|page=3|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227052931/https://www.unhcr.org/refworld/pdfid/42f736424.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2005年，波黑塞族领袖公开敦促卡拉季奇投降，他表示卡拉季奇的在逃会阻碍波斯尼亚和塞尔维亚两国在政治和经济上的发展。在五月份一次失败的突袭过后，北约士兵于2005年7月7日逮捕了拉多万·卡拉季奇的儿子亚历山大。不过他们在10天后释放了亞歷山大。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/4659319.stm|title=Nato troops arrest Karadzic's son|publisher=BBC|date=2005-07-07|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2017-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170806102842/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/europe/4659319.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月28日。卡拉季奇的妻子呼吁她的丈夫投降。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4725923.stm|title=Karadzic's wife urges surrender|publisher=BBC|date=2005-07-29|accessdate=2010-01-04|archive-date=2021-02-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225113301/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/europe/4725923.stm|dead-url=no}} See also:{{cite web|url=http://arhiva.glas-javnosti.rs/arhiva/2005/07/29/srpski/P05072807.shtml|title=Radovane, predaj se!|publisher=Yugoslavia News|date=2005-07-29|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052916/http://arhiva.glas-javnosti.rs/arhiva/2005/07/29/srpski/P05072807.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

BBC报道称，2005年有人在[[福查|福查]]附近苏捷斯卡国家公园边界上看到过卡拉季奇，报道中评论，西方国家情报机关知道卡拉季奇和姆拉迪奇在哪里，可英美两国政府为了避免伤亡不对他们采取抓捕行动。<ref>{{cite news|title=Why Bosnia's most wanted run free|publisher=BBC|date=28 June 2008|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/from_our_own_correspondent/7477912.stm|accessdate=2015-07-13|archive-date=2020-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201214004054/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/programmes/from_our_own_correspondent/7477912.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1999年起，<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.b92.net/eng/news/crimes.php?yyyy=2008&mm=07&dd=25&nav_id=52206|title=Karadžić became Dabić in 1999|date=2008-07-28|newspaper=B92|accessdate=2015-07-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140422142243/http://www.b92.net/eng/news/crimes.php?yyyy=2008&mm=07&dd=25&nav_id=52206|archivedate=22 April 2014}}</ref>卡拉季奇将自己伪装成了一个“[[新纪元运动|新纪元]]医药专家”在民间行医。他名片上印着的假名是“D.D. David”，开头的字母缩写明显是“Dragan Dabić”的缩写。也有官员说，卡拉季奇有时会使用“Dr. Dragan David Dabić”这个名字。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.b92.net/eng/news/politics.php?yyyy=2008&mm=07&dd=22&nav_id=52109|title=Karadžić "practiced alternative medicine"|date=2008-07-22|newspaper=B92|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220164417/http://www.b92.net/eng/news/politics.php?yyyy=2008&mm=07&dd=22&nav_id=52109|archivedate=2014-02-20}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/karadzicevi-savjeti-kod-problema-sa-seksom-najbolja-je-terapija-u-paru/395880.aspx|title=Karadžićevi savjeti: Kod problema sa seksom najbolja je terapija u paru (Karadžić's tips: For problems with sex the best therapy is with couples)|date=2008-07-22|newspaper=Vijestinet|deadurl=no|language=hr|archivedate=2019-12-01|accessdate=2016-06-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201104856/https://www.index.hr/vijesti/clanak/karadzicevi-savjeti-kod-problema-sa-seksom-najbolja-je-terapija-u-paru/395880.aspx}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.wral.com/news/national_world/world/story/3250779|title=Karadzic hid in plain view to elude capture|date=2008-07-22|publisher=WRAL|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080731230240/http://www.wral.com/news/national_world/world/story/3250779/|archivedate=2008-07-31|author=Stojanovic, Dusan}}</ref>他曾在数百人面前演讲，以宣传他卖的药。在他的个人网站上，他说，他可以用“人体量子能量”治愈[[性病|性病]]和[[性功能障碍|性功能障碍]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.psy-help-energy.com|title=Human Quantum Energy|accessdate=2008-07-25|publisher=PSY Help Energy|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080724223555/http://www.psy-help-energy.com/|archivedate=2008-07-24|deadurl=yes}}</ref>据报道，2007年5月，卡拉季奇在维也纳逃脱了奥地利警方的抓捕。当时他冒充成了一个叫佩塔尔·格鲁马茨的克罗地亚籍药贩子。<ref name="奥地利通讯社">{{cite web|url=http://www.apa.at/cms/site/news_item.html?channel=CH0069&doc=CMS1217014246968|title=Karadzic nannte sich "Peter Schauspieler"|accessdate=2008-07-26|publisher=奥地利通讯社|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110531200419/http://www.apa.at/cms/site/news_item.html?channel=CH0069&doc=CMS1217014246968|archivedate=2011-05-31}}</ref>奥地利警方在一次与某个过失杀人案有关的行动中，碰到了卡拉季奇并同卡拉季奇进行了谈话，但他们没有认出卡拉季奇的真实身份。卡拉季奇持有克罗地亚护照并宣称他是来奥地利实习的。<ref name="奥地利通讯社"/>奥地利警方见他面对警察时十分冷静，又积极配合提问，就不再深究。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSL543550020080725?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0|title=Karadzic escaped arrest in Austria last year|accessdate=26 July 2008|publisher=Reuters|first=Boris|last=Groendahl|date=2008-07-25|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308202604/https://www.reuters.com/article/worldNews/idUSL543550020080725?pageNumber=1&virtualBrandChannel=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过这条消息真实度存疑，因为一名叫佩塔尔·格鲁马茨的医生宣称他曾在维也纳被警察叫去谈话。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.euronews.net/en/article/28/07/2008/radovan-karadzic-may-not-have-been-in-vienna|title=Radovan Karadzic may not have been in Vienna|publisher=EuroNews|access-date=2016-07-03|archive-date=2008-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080903135500/http://www.euronews.net/en/article/28/07/2008/radovan-karadzic-may-not-have-been-in-vienna/|dead-url=no}}</ref>卡拉季奇的侄子Dragan说，卡拉季奇曾以佩塔尔·格鲁马茨的名义参加一场足球赛。<ref name="corriere.it" />
==审讯==
=== 逮捕及审讯 ===
2008年，正以[[替代医学|替代医学]]专家身份在[[維也納|维也纳]]和[[贝尔格莱德|贝尔格莱德]]两地行医的卡拉季奇，於贝尔格莱德被捕。<ref name="BBC-2008-07-22" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.wtop.com/?nid=383&sid=1444312|title=Karadzic interviewed about details of his arrest|accessdate=26 July 2008|agency=Associated Press|archive-date=2008-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080731050354/http://www.wtop.com/?nid=383&sid=1444312|dead-url=no}}</ref>7月30日，卡拉季奇被送至海牙的前南斯拉夫问题国际刑事法庭。在第一次审讯中，卡拉季奇对妻子说出了他的恐惧：“如果霍尔布鲁克后悔之前在这个法庭上没有人被判死刑，想要拿我开刀的话，我想知道他的手臂能不能够到我。”<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/07/31/AR2008073100363.html?hpid=moreheadlines|title=Karadzic appears at UN court|date=1 August 2008|work=Washington Post|accessdate=20 December 2010|archive-date=2019-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190822115046/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2008/07/31/AR2008073100363.html?hpid=moreheadlines|dead-url=no}}</ref>同时，他说，他之所以能逃亡13年之久，是因为他与霍尔布鲁克达成了交易。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gZy0ZegDYcy8yLg1vT7wnZjJcRvw|title=Holbrooke promised no ICTY trial: Karadzic|accessdate=20 December 2010|date=1 August 2008|publisher=Google|agency=AFP|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100910070936/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5gZy0ZegDYcy8yLg1vT7wnZjJcRvw|archivedate=2010年9月10日}}</ref>他也对美国前国务卿马德琳·奥尔布莱特做出了同样的指控。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5hDjfrs7G6ubbn16kfGGmiJuCRu0Q|title=US wants me dead: Karadžić|date=1 August 2008|publisher=Google|accessdate=20 December 2010|agency=AFP|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110520153719/http://afp.google.com/article/ALeqM5hDjfrs7G6ubbn16kfGGmiJuCRu0Q|archivedate=2011年5月20日}}</ref>Muhamed Sacirbey，当时的波斯尼亚外长宣称，他们是在1996年7月达成这项交易的。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail.aspx?id=65316&sectionid=351020606|title=Karadzic-Holbrooke deal confirmed|accessdate=20 December 2010|publisher=Presstv.ir|archive-date=2016-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105201803/http://www.presstv.ir/detail.aspx?id=65316&sectionid=351020606|dead-url=no}}</ref>

